PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of ANNE WHELAN of St. John's, Newfoundland and Labrador, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Business Development Bank of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of one year, in the place of Brian Hayward, effective June 18, 2016.
